sec.p: The authors thank UCSF leaders Eugene Washington and Sally Marshall, and Coro leader Maureen McNutty, for their collective vision and foresight in initially creating the collaboration. The authors also thank Susan Shain, previous CEO of Coro, Nancy Schemick, Coro Adjunct Faculty, and Melanie Fisch at UCSF for their contributions to earlier phases of the collaboration, Janice Cheng for her contribution in the initial phase of qualitative and quantitative analyses, and Genanne Walsh for editorial reviews of the manuscript.
